cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.MM, cs.CV, cs.LG 

The paper deals with language translation using neural networks, audio and visual analysis, and video communication. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves data analysis and machine learning, which could fall under cs.SD (Sound and Data). The use of video chat corpora and audio-visual communication system could be categorized under cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also involves image and video processing, which could fall under cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the development of translation models using neural networks could be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning).
